{"tid":622294,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新華社文章指美國貿易「霸凌」政策　嚴重踐踏契約精神","createTime":"2018-04-09T04:56:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-09T11:51:42.000Z","uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"90b7ac038d53a3b3d3e792d5eb00d984c7da3c86","tid":622294,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T04:56:19.000Z","msg":"新華社文章指美國貿易「霸凌」政策　嚴重踐踏契約精神<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1390089-20180409.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1390089-20180409.htm&d=Mq2wWObIBZX4gLhDb%2F3GPMn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=8e6c5251\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1390089-20180409.htm&h=f02ceed7\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1390089-20180409.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n新華社發表署名文章，指美國貿易「霸凌」政策，有違世貿組織原則和精神，嚴重踐踏國際商業社會秉持的契約精神。<br />\n<br />\n文章指出，美國提出加徵關稅等措施，是對多邊貿易體系公然挑釁；雖然美國是世界第一大經濟體，但就基於錯誤事實依據和偏差的統計，進行貿易脅迫，利用優勢貿易地位，強迫貿易夥伴犧牲利益。<br />\n<br />\n新華社說，美方貿易逆差，同當地經濟結構性缺陷，以及管制高科技出口密切相關，美國自身經濟有問題，但就向外尋找「代罪羔羊」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afd237edc5320312130a87052d04e39424903324","tid":622294,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T04:58:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e449932c1a39d1e4409c150d1c762f497e6dacf","tid":622294,"uid":4917,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T04:58:31.000Z","msg":"支那有遵守過世貿嘅要求咩？"},{"pid":"7a05620d98c73e92ad51059d75b2a8e5f37245c2","tid":622294,"uid":171788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T05:00:14.000Z","msg":"American Pig ! <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img